quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  22,49,"E re: “Oho batho! Ke rometsoe ho lona feela ho fana thlokomeliso e hlakileng"
  22,50,"Bohle ba kholoang ba etsa liketso tse lokileng, ts’oarelo e teng bakeng sa bona `moho le nala e babatsehang"
  22,51,"Empa haele ba tsitlaletseng khahlanong le lits’enolo tsa Rona, – e tla ba balekane ba Mollo.”"
  22,52,"Ha Re’a s’o ka Re romella moromuoa, kapa moporofeta pele ho uena, ebe eba Satane ha a mo hoka-hoke ka malepa. Empa Allah U hlakola sohle seo Stane a se etsang. Allah U phethahatsa lits’enolo tsa Hae. Hobane Allah U tletse tsebo, U Seli"
  22,53,"E le hore A tle A etse seo liabolosi a se etsang teko ho bao lipelo tsa bona ho tletseng maloetse, le bao lipelo tsa bona li thatafetseng, – Ruri! Baetsalibe ba karohanong e totobetseng, –"
  22,54,"Le ba nehiloeng tsebo ba tle ba tsebe hore ke ‘nete e tsoang ho Mong`a hau, ba tle ba kholoe ho eona le lipelo tsa bona li tle li inehele ka boikokobetso ho Eena. Hobane! Ruri Allah U tataisa bohle ba kholoang tseleng e totobetseng"
  22,55,"Bohle ba hanyetsang tumelo ba ke ke ba khaotsa ho ba le khoao holim’a eona, ho fihlela hora e ba oela ka ts’ohanyetso, kapa ba tloha ba oeloa ke Letsatsi la Tlokotsi"
  22,56,"Matla a Puso mohla letsatsi leo, e tla be e le a Allah feela. Ke Eena Ea tla ahlola lipakeng tsa bona. Haele ba tla beng ba kholoa, ba etsa liketso tse lokileng ba tla kena ka har’a Lirapa tsa Nyakallo"
  22,57,"Ba hanyetsang tumelo, ba latola lits’enolo tsa Rona, ho teng Kahlolo e soabisang"